[SPEAKER_00] i bacili u savu.

551
00:29:19,259 --> 00:29:20,180
[SPEAKER_00] Njih oko sto.

552
00:29:20,180 --> 00:29:21,619
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kaže,

553
