576
00:29:50,339 --> 00:29:51,039
[SPEAKER_00] bili u savu.

577
00:29:51,039 --> 00:29:51,440
[SPEAKER_00] A ovdje imamo,

578
00:29:51,440 --> 00:29:52,559
[SPEAKER_00] znači, dokaz,

579
00:29:52,660 --> 00:29:54,460
[SPEAKER_00] izvješće komunističke partije,

580
00:29:54,460 --> 00:29:55,819
[SPEAKER_00] Bosna i Hercegovine,

581
