583
00:29:57,160 --> 00:29:57,720
[SPEAKER_00] Da su to oni radili.

584
00:29:57,720 --> 00:29:58,819
[SPEAKER_00] Oni to pišu.

585
00:29:58,819 --> 00:30:00,140
