588
00:30:04,279 --> 00:30:05,859
[SPEAKER_00] Kao i ovdje što su napisali.

589
00:30:05,859 --> 00:30:07,240
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, jesu djeca ubijene,

590
00:30:07,240 --> 00:30:08,059
[SPEAKER_00] ali nisu naša.

591
00:30:08,059 --> 00:30:08,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ili ovo,

592
00:30:08,980 --> 00:30:10,339
[SPEAKER_00] vi možete ubijati ljude,

593
00:30:10,339 --> 00:30:11,180
[SPEAKER_00] ali nemojte tako ubijati

594
