[SPEAKER_00] da šteti pokretu,

595
00:30:12,099 --> 00:30:13,259
[SPEAKER_00] da šteti vlasti.

596
00:30:13,259 --> 00:30:14,339
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, kažem,

597
00:30:14,339 --> 00:30:15,180
[SPEAKER_00] jer to su u principu

598
00:30:15,180 --> 00:30:16,140
