[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje.

602
00:30:20,240 --> 00:30:21,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ne smemo zaboraviti

603
00:30:21,619 --> 00:30:23,700
[SPEAKER_00] opet kad možemo se vratiti

604
00:30:23,700 --> 00:30:24,220
[SPEAKER_00] na Zagreb,

605
00:30:24,220 --> 00:30:25,539
[SPEAKER_00] što su u Zagrebu radili.

606
00:30:25,539 --> 00:30:26,859
[SPEAKER_00] Radili su koji svugdje dalje.

607
00:30:26,859 --> 00:30:27,920
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su naročito voljeli

608
00:30:27,920 --> 00:30:28,660
