611
00:30:30,380 --> 00:30:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] da je bila bitka za ranjenike,

612
00:30:31,539 --> 00:30:33,359
[SPEAKER_00] ali imamo dokaza puno

613
00:30:33,359 --> 00:30:34,720
[SPEAKER_00] da su ubijali ranjenike

614
00:30:34,720 --> 00:30:35,680
[SPEAKER_00] o sveti duh Zagreba.

615
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:36,779
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su odveženi na Jazovku,

616
00:30:36,779 --> 00:30:37,440
