619
00:30:45,799 --> 00:30:46,900
[SPEAKER_00] proteza i tako dalje.

620
00:30:46,900 --> 00:30:49,019
[SPEAKER_00] To je dokaz da su ubijali ranjenike.

621
00:30:49,019 --> 00:30:51,099
[SPEAKER_00] Ali imamo još svježi dokaz

622
00:30:51,099 --> 00:30:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] da su ubijali ranjenike

623
