625
00:30:54,240 --> 00:30:54,579
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam,

626
00:30:54,579 --> 00:30:55,880
[SPEAKER_00] nekakva posebna strast.

627
00:30:55,880 --> 00:30:56,880
[SPEAKER_00] To je sad Vukovar.

628
00:30:56,880 --> 00:30:58,220
[SPEAKER_00] Opet bolnica,

629
00:30:58,220 --> 00:30:59,339
[SPEAKER_00] opet ranjenici,

630
00:30:59,339 --> 00:31:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] opet ubijanje.

631
00:31:00,119 --> 00:31:01,099
[SPEAKER_00] I opet Jugoslavinska armija.

632
00:31:01,099 --> 00:31:03,240
[SPEAKER_00] Opet Jugoslavinska armija.

633
00:31:03,240 --> 00:31:06,200
[SPEAKER_00] I opet antifašisti,

634
00:31:06,200 --> 00:31:06,559
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne znam.

635
00:31:06,559 --> 00:31:08,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ako su to antifašisti,

636
00:31:08,019 --> 00:31:08,779
