637
00:31:08,779 --> 00:31:09,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ja to ne želim.

638
00:31:09,420 --> 00:31:10,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne želim na taj antifašizam.

639
00:31:10,799 --> 00:31:11,359
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno.

640
00:31:15,180 --> 00:31:17,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ubijati ljude koji su ranjenike.

641
00:31:17,200 --> 00:31:18,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ubijati ranjenike.

642
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:20,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je istina ovo što ste rekli.

643
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:21,440
[SPEAKER_01] Ali dakle,

644
00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:25,160
[SPEAKER_01] osim tih koji su odvedeni

645
00:31:25,160 --> 00:31:27,039
[SPEAKER_01] sa Svetog Duha na Jazovki,

646
