[SPEAKER_01] odvedeni su i ubijani

647
00:31:28,859 --> 00:31:29,660
[SPEAKER_01] i na licu mjesta

648
00:31:29,660 --> 00:31:31,160
[SPEAKER_01] i odvođeni iz bolnice

649
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:32,400
[SPEAKER_01] se stara Milosebnica.

650
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:33,500
[SPEAKER_01] Da tamo su isto ubijani.

651
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:34,039
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

652
00:31:34,039 --> 00:31:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ubijani su,

653
00:31:35,460 --> 00:31:36,859
[SPEAKER_00] recimo ja sam naješao u Travniku,

654
00:31:36,859 --> 00:31:38,039
[SPEAKER_00] isto baš u tim dokumentima.

655
00:31:38,039 --> 00:31:39,220
[SPEAKER_00] To oni priznaju čak.

656
00:31:39,220 --> 00:31:40,119
[SPEAKER_00] U Travniku,

657
00:31:40,119 --> 00:31:41,200
[SPEAKER_00] isto kad su ušli ime dokaze,

658
00:31:41,200 --> 00:31:41,859
[SPEAKER_00] onda imao ođaku,

659
00:31:41,859 --> 00:31:42,920
[SPEAKER_00] su isto ubijali ranjenike.

660
00:31:42,940 --> 00:31:43,940
[SPEAKER_01] To je bio model.

661
00:31:43,940 --> 00:31:44,900
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo pravilo.

662
00:31:44,900 --> 00:31:46,319
[SPEAKER_00] To je bila naredba.

663
00:31:46,319 --> 00:31:47,339
[SPEAKER_00] Naredba, tako.

664
00:31:47,339 --> 00:31:47,819
[SPEAKER_00] E upravo to.

665
00:31:47,819 --> 00:31:49,220
[SPEAKER_01] Mi ste ju pokazali naredba.

666
00:31:49,220 --> 00:31:50,799
[SPEAKER_00] S tim što ne piše tu za bolnice.

667
00:31:50,799 --> 00:31:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] Možda ima druga za bolnice.

668
00:31:52,059 --> 00:31:52,319
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

669
00:31:52,319 --> 00:31:53,299
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je za grad.

670
00:31:53,299 --> 00:31:54,619
[SPEAKER_01] Kako zatvoriš grad,

671
00:31:54,619 --> 00:31:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] pobiješ sve sliste

672
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:59,160
[SPEAKER_01] i onda pacificiraš ih na taj način.

673
00:31:59,160 --> 00:32:00,279
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da evo,

674
00:32:00,279 --> 00:32:01,279
[SPEAKER_00] uglavnom,

675
00:32:01,279 --> 00:32:02,980
[SPEAKER_00] mi se vraćamo opet,

676
00:32:02,980 --> 00:32:03,940
[SPEAKER_00] mi se nismo suočili

677
00:32:03,940 --> 00:32:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] s tom komunističkom prošloću

678
00:32:05,380 --> 00:32:06,680
[SPEAKER_00] i nije došlo do lustracije.

679
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:09,319
[SPEAKER_00] I u stvari ono što se dogodilo,

680
00:32:09,319 --> 00:32:12,180
[SPEAKER_01] da su žrtve fašizma,

681
00:32:12,940 --> 00:32:14,660
[SPEAKER_01] te žrtve su sve

682
00:32:14,660 --> 00:32:17,400
[SPEAKER_01] dobile satisfakciju kao žrtve.

683
00:32:17,400 --> 00:32:19,819
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, priznalo se u redu,

684
00:32:19,819 --> 00:32:21,299
[SPEAKER_01] ovi su ljudi ubijeni,

685
00:32:21,299 --> 00:32:22,660
[SPEAKER_01] to nije u redu,

686
00:32:22,660 --> 00:32:24,099
[SPEAKER_01] to je nepošteno,

687
00:32:24,099 --> 00:32:24,940
[SPEAKER_01] to je zločin

688
00:32:24,940 --> 00:32:26,759
[SPEAKER_01] i nitko ga nije imao pravo raditi

689
00:32:26,759 --> 00:32:27,460
[SPEAKER_01] i opravdavati.

690
00:32:27,460 --> 00:32:28,700
[SPEAKER_01] Nikoga niti opravdavati.

691
00:32:28,700 --> 00:32:31,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ali žrtve komunizma i partizana

692
00:32:31,599 --> 00:32:33,039
[SPEAKER_01] koji su u konačnici,

693
00:32:33,039 --> 00:32:35,920
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, ustaštvo je trajalo 4 godina,

694
00:32:35,920 --> 00:32:37,740
[SPEAKER_01] ovo je trajalo 45 godina,

695
00:32:37,740 --> 00:32:39,400
[SPEAKER_01] žrtve tog režima,

696
00:32:39,400 --> 00:32:41,279
[SPEAKER_01] kao da se nisu dogodile.

697
00:32:41,380 --> 00:32:43,559
[SPEAKER_01] Mi imamo bivšu ministricu vanjskih poslova,

698
00:32:43,559 --> 00:32:44,200
[SPEAKER_01] Vesno Pustić,

699
00:32:44,200 --> 00:32:47,539
[SPEAKER_01] koja je rekla da ljudi koji su ubijeni

700
00:32:47,539 --> 00:32:48,660
[SPEAKER_01] na križnom putu,

701
00:32:48,660 --> 00:32:50,940
[SPEAKER_01] da nisu bili krivi,

702
00:32:50,940 --> 00:32:51,980
[SPEAKER_01] da ne bi bili tamo.

703
00:32:51,980 --> 00:32:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ona je brani

704
00:32:54,000 --> 00:32:56,440
[SPEAKER_01] iz pozicije političke u Hrvatskoj,

705
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:59,039
[SPEAKER_01] ona je branila zločine nad ljudima

706
00:32:59,039 --> 00:33:00,380
[SPEAKER_01] koji su bili ratni zarobljeniji.

707
00:33:00,480 --> 00:33:02,079
[SPEAKER_00] Za pravnog aspekta je, koliko ja znam,

708
00:33:02,079 --> 00:33:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] pravo, kažnjivo je opravdavati zločin.

709
00:33:04,420 --> 00:33:05,039
[SPEAKER_00] To je kažnjivo.

710
00:33:05,039 --> 00:33:08,839
[SPEAKER_00] A ovo je neupitno zločin.

711
00:33:08,839 --> 00:33:10,900
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, kažem,

712
00:33:10,900 --> 00:33:13,380
[SPEAKER_00] što se tiče tih komunističkih zločina,

713
00:33:13,380 --> 00:33:16,359
[SPEAKER_00] to vapije do neba.

714
00:33:16,359 --> 00:33:17,240
[SPEAKER_00] Evo recimo, kad gledate,

715
00:33:17,240 --> 00:33:18,880
[SPEAKER_00] vi nećete naći za vrijeme NDH,

716
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:21,140
[SPEAKER_00] nijedno stratište kao huda jama.

717
00:33:21,559 --> 00:33:23,339
[SPEAKER_00] Zamislite, zazivati žive ljude

718
00:33:23,339 --> 00:33:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] i ne dati im hranu, vodu,

719
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] to ni u Auschwitzu nema.

720
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:28,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to što su oni radili,

721
00:33:28,380 --> 00:33:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] to ni nacisti nisu radili.

722
00:33:30,000 --> 00:33:31,599
[SPEAKER_00] Jer, u principu,

723
00:33:31,599 --> 00:33:33,059
[SPEAKER_00] vi kad čovjeka ubije,

724
00:33:33,059 --> 00:33:33,759
[SPEAKER_00] u stvari ubijete.

725
00:33:33,759 --> 00:33:35,700
[SPEAKER_00] Ta je smrt trenutna.

726
00:33:35,700 --> 00:33:38,259
[SPEAKER_00] A zamislite, kad vi umirete 15-20 dana,

727
00:33:38,259 --> 00:33:39,880
[SPEAKER_00] umirete u najvećim bolivima,

728
00:33:39,880 --> 00:33:41,480
[SPEAKER_00] u mraku, u vlazi.

729
00:33:41,480 --> 00:33:43,480
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjeli smo da onaj jedan čovjek je pokušao,

730
00:33:43,480 --> 00:33:44,700
[SPEAKER_00] razbio je ne znam koliko,

731
00:33:44,700 --> 00:33:45,319
[SPEAKER_00] sedam metara,

732
00:33:45,319 --> 00:33:47,019
[SPEAKER_00] možda može trebalo tri metara da probije,

733
00:33:47,259 --> 00:33:49,740
[SPEAKER_00] pa da se neki koji su bili izražljivi spasa i tako dalje.

734
00:33:49,740 --> 00:33:51,200
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjeli smo tamo da ima žena,

735
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:51,880
[SPEAKER_00] ima djece.

736
00:33:51,880 --> 00:33:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Djece, pletenice,

737
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:54,380
[SPEAKER_01] one koje su izvučene.

738
00:33:54,380 --> 00:33:56,579
[SPEAKER_00] To nema ni u Auschwitzu,

739
00:33:56,579 --> 00:33:59,240
[SPEAKER_00] ali kod jugoslavijskih komunista to ima.

740
00:33:59,240 --> 00:34:01,339
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da...

741
00:34:01,339 --> 00:34:03,240
[SPEAKER_01] I to se prešućuje.

742
00:34:03,240 --> 00:34:05,220
[SPEAKER_01] O tome se ne želi govoriti.

743
00:34:05,220 --> 00:34:07,119
[SPEAKER_01] Kad se govori o Titu ili o Jugoslavi,

744
00:34:07,119 --> 00:34:08,980
[SPEAKER_01] nastoji se stalno veličati

745
00:34:08,980 --> 00:34:10,579
[SPEAKER_01] upravo one koji su za to odgovorili.

746
00:34:10,579 --> 00:34:12,300
[SPEAKER_00] Koji su to napravili.

747
00:34:12,300 --> 00:34:12,780
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

748
00:34:12,780 --> 00:34:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] Kažem, ja često isto znam napomenuti,

749
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:17,460
[SPEAKER_00] evo, recimo, mi kad smo radili knjigu

750
00:34:17,460 --> 00:34:18,860
[SPEAKER_00] Prikrivena grobišta Đakoviština,

751
00:34:18,860 --> 00:34:21,940
[SPEAKER_00] na slovnu stranicu smo stavili Ambroziju.

752
00:34:21,940 --> 00:34:23,179
[SPEAKER_00] To je, u svari,

753
00:34:23,179 --> 00:34:24,719
[SPEAKER_00] to je možda i vaša struka.

754
00:34:24,719 --> 00:34:25,320
[SPEAKER_00] Što je Ambrozija?

755
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:27,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ambrozija je nekakva trava, korov,

756
00:34:27,039 --> 00:34:29,460
[SPEAKER_00] koja je beskornista uništava sve oko sebe

757
00:34:29,460 --> 00:34:30,320
[SPEAKER_00] i tamo gdje dođe,

758
00:34:30,320 --> 00:34:31,860
[SPEAKER_00] ništa ne raste.

759
00:34:31,860 --> 00:34:33,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ali na Ardiju je nazvao Partizanka,

760
00:34:33,340 --> 00:34:34,119
[SPEAKER_00] nije Domobranka.

761
00:34:34,119 --> 00:34:35,920
[SPEAKER_00] Jer sad, to govori...

762
00:34:35,920 --> 00:34:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sad, kog će oni otkriviti?

763
00:34:38,000 --> 00:34:40,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ime Partizanka imate na internetu.

764
00:34:40,440 --> 00:34:42,260
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, na ovih pedi, kad stavite Ambrozija,

765
00:34:42,260 --> 00:34:43,119
[SPEAKER_00] piše Partizanka.

766
00:34:43,119 --> 00:34:45,420
[SPEAKER_00] A onda kad piše, znamo,

767
00:34:45,420 --> 00:34:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] kad čak imate i zakon da se Ambrozija mora uništavat,

768
00:34:48,559 --> 00:34:51,139
[SPEAKER_00] i sada, ako ona je Partizanka,

769
00:34:51,139 --> 00:34:51,980
[SPEAKER_00] njima ćete nazvat antifašistica.

770
00:34:51,980 --> 00:34:52,900
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

771
00:34:52,900 --> 00:34:54,440
[SPEAKER_00] I zamislite, sadašnje vlasti traže

772
00:34:54,440 --> 00:34:55,699
[SPEAKER_00] da se uništava antifašistica.

773
00:34:55,699 --> 00:34:56,800
[SPEAKER_00] To je strava, korov,

774
00:34:56,800 --> 00:34:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji uništavaju oko sebe.

775
00:34:58,000 --> 00:35:01,019
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da, ali zanimljivo je ovo,

776
00:35:01,019 --> 00:35:02,760
[SPEAKER_01] opet mi je ovo zanimljivo kako ste rekli,

777
00:35:02,760 --> 00:35:05,480
[SPEAKER_01] da su oni, u stvari, dan ulazka u Đakovo,

778
00:35:05,480 --> 00:35:08,679
[SPEAKER_01] kada su pobili toliko ljudi u Đakovu,

779
00:35:08,679 --> 00:35:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] ušli su Njemci, nije bilo pobijeni.

780
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:12,440
[SPEAKER_01] Nije bilo.

781
00:35:12,440 --> 00:35:15,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ušli su Partizani, popisi pobijeni.

782
00:35:15,119 --> 00:35:17,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ali onda to druga vrsta nasilja,

783
00:35:17,960 --> 00:35:21,139
[SPEAKER_01] gdje oni taj grad masovnih ubojstava,

784
00:35:21,480 --> 00:35:24,139
[SPEAKER_01] taj datum proglase danom grada.

785
00:35:24,139 --> 00:35:27,280
[SPEAKER_01] Kako je to presija ona na drugoj razini sada?

786
00:35:27,280 --> 00:35:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da on tebe tjera i tvoju djecu,

787
00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:29,940
[SPEAKER_01] djecu ubijenih,

788
00:35:29,940 --> 00:35:32,500
[SPEAKER_01] da je to dan kad se slavi u Đakovu.

789
00:35:32,500 --> 00:35:34,119
[SPEAKER_00] To je isto kao da sad u Auschwitzu

790
00:35:34,119 --> 00:35:36,139
[SPEAKER_00] obježavaju dan kad je osnovan Auschwitz,

791
00:35:36,139 --> 00:35:37,539
[SPEAKER_00] a to bude dan grada Auschwitz.

792
00:35:37,539 --> 00:35:38,079
[SPEAKER_01] Traž.

793
00:35:38,079 --> 00:35:38,940
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, to je to...

794
00:35:38,940 --> 00:35:40,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je ovo, ista metoda

795
00:35:40,480 --> 00:35:45,139
[SPEAKER_01] kojom oni neprekidno svoje ideološke postulate,

796
00:35:45,139 --> 00:35:46,880
[SPEAKER_01] ono što su oni postavili,

797
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:50,280
[SPEAKER_01] daljnjim nasiljem nastoje opravdati.

798
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:51,599
[SPEAKER_00] Pa dobra činjenica je,

799
00:35:51,599 --> 00:35:53,179
[SPEAKER_00] mislim, mi smo svjedociti tog vremena,

800
00:35:53,179 --> 00:35:55,300
[SPEAKER_00] znači 90. godine kad se dogodio,

801
00:35:55,300 --> 00:35:58,219
[SPEAKER_00] kad se dogodio domovinski rat i tako dalje,

802
00:35:58,219 --> 00:35:59,820
[SPEAKER_00] nije došlo do lustracije,

803
00:35:59,820 --> 00:36:02,539
[SPEAKER_00] iako ja znam često puta kak se na to doživio.

804
00:36:02,539 --> 00:36:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, Hrvatska je nastala,

805
00:36:04,199 --> 00:36:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] nakon onog 14. godinja sa Komuniške partije,

806
00:36:06,460 --> 00:36:08,380
[SPEAKER_00] kad su se komunisti međusobno posvađali.

807
00:36:08,380 --> 00:36:10,500
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, srpski komunisti se posvađali

808
00:36:10,500 --> 00:36:12,039
[SPEAKER_00] sa slovenskim komunistima

809
00:36:12,039 --> 00:36:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] i sa pola naših komunista.

810
00:36:13,480 --> 00:36:15,079
[SPEAKER_00] I oni kad su se posvađali,

811
00:36:15,079 --> 00:36:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] jedina komunistička partija koja nije htjela Jugoslaviju,

812
00:36:18,440 --> 00:36:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] to je bila Komuniška partija Srbije.

813
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] Što ona htjela?

814
00:36:20,519 --> 00:36:21,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je htjela Veliku Srbiju.

815
00:36:21,860 --> 00:36:23,559
[SPEAKER_00] A jugoslavenski komunisti,

816
00:36:23,559 --> 00:36:24,159
[SPEAKER_00] oni su htjeli,

817
00:36:24,159 --> 00:36:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] ne hrvatski komunisti,

818
00:36:25,380 --> 00:36:27,619
[SPEAKER_00] hrvatski komunisti su htjeli Jugoslaviju.

819
00:36:27,619 --> 00:36:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da, pa naravno.

820
00:36:28,699 --> 00:36:29,860
[SPEAKER_00] I zato je nastala Hrvatska.

821
00:36:29,860 --> 00:36:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatska nije nastala voljom hrvatskih komunista.

822
00:36:32,559 --> 00:36:33,239
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je nastala,

823
00:36:33,239 --> 00:36:34,320
[SPEAKER_00] ona je nastala,

824
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:37,820
[SPEAKER_00] što samo ne postojanje Jugoslavije,

825
00:36:37,820 --> 00:36:39,699
[SPEAKER_00] znači, nameće postojanje Hrvatske.

826
00:36:39,699 --> 00:36:41,519
[SPEAKER_00] To je gospodin Hasa Begović često kaže.

827
00:36:41,519 --> 00:36:44,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, postojanje Hrvatske je negacija Jugoslavije

828
00:36:44,880 --> 00:36:45,539
[SPEAKER_00] ili obratno.

829
00:36:45,539 --> 00:36:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, znači, nisu naši komunisti

830
00:36:47,539 --> 00:36:48,340
[SPEAKER_00] uopće zaslužni,

831
00:36:48,340 --> 00:36:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] što se dogodili,

832
00:36:49,119 --> 00:36:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] što je Hrvatska postala država,

833
00:36:52,000 --> 00:36:53,039
[SPEAKER_00] a između ostalog,

834
00:36:53,039 --> 00:36:54,320
[SPEAKER_00] zašto su se oni borili za Hrvatsku?

835
00:36:54,739 --> 00:36:57,119
[SPEAKER_00] Zato što bi ovi su bili protiv njih,

836
00:36:57,119 --> 00:36:58,820
[SPEAKER_00] oni bi stradali od srpskih komunista.

837
00:36:58,820 --> 00:36:59,900
[SPEAKER_01] Da, kao što je bila borba

838
00:36:59,900 --> 00:37:01,639
[SPEAKER_01] između Staljina i Tita.

839
00:37:01,639 --> 00:37:02,920
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, pa nije to bila borba

840
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] kako se kasnije prikazivalo na sušku.

841
00:37:04,739 --> 00:37:05,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ino Jugoslavena i Rusa.

842
00:37:05,659 --> 00:37:06,460
[SPEAKER_01] Jugoslavena i Rusa.

843
00:37:06,460 --> 00:37:07,579
[SPEAKER_01] Da, tako je, tako je.

844
00:37:07,579 --> 00:37:09,239
[SPEAKER_00] To je znači unutrastranačka borba.

845
00:37:09,239 --> 00:37:10,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ili da je Tito Staljin smeto

846
00:37:10,699 --> 00:37:11,780
[SPEAKER_01] ili je on bio zločinac.

847
00:37:11,780 --> 00:37:14,219
[SPEAKER_01] Ma ne, već zato što bi Staljin njega maknuo.

848
00:37:14,219 --> 00:37:16,219
[SPEAKER_01] To su sve bile borbe među...

849
00:37:16,219 --> 00:37:18,760
[SPEAKER_00] Unutar iste bande.

850
00:37:18,760 --> 00:37:20,480
[SPEAKER_00] Najišao sam isto na puno dokumenta

851
00:37:20,480 --> 00:37:22,300
[SPEAKER_00] koji govore istog krivotvorina

852
00:37:22,300 --> 00:37:23,619
[SPEAKER_00] da je Tito rekao Staljin.

853
00:37:23,619 --> 00:37:26,860
[SPEAKER_00] Svi dokumenti govore da je Staljin njemu rekao ne.

854
00:37:26,860 --> 00:37:29,500
[SPEAKER_00] To sam čak čitao neki historiografi

855
00:37:29,500 --> 00:37:30,679
[SPEAKER_00] i to navode u slove u Srbiji.

856
00:37:30,679 --> 00:37:31,139
[SPEAKER_00] Neću otvoriti.

857
00:37:31,139 --> 00:37:32,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, uglavnom, Tito je htio da se Koruška

858
00:37:32,960 --> 00:37:34,019
[SPEAKER_00] pripoji Jugoslavi.

859
00:37:34,019 --> 00:37:36,400
[SPEAKER_00] Htio je da se pripoji ovaj dio

860
00:37:36,400 --> 00:37:37,559
[SPEAKER_00] Mađarske Jugoslavi.

861
00:37:37,559 --> 00:37:40,119
[SPEAKER_00] I htio je da se pripoji Albanija Jugoslavi.

862
00:37:40,119 --> 00:37:41,400
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je njemu Staljin rekao ne može.

863
00:37:41,860 --> 00:37:44,980
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da u stvari njemu Staljin rekao ne.

864
00:37:44,980 --> 00:37:46,599
[SPEAKER_00] A između oslovog Tito je tražio

865
00:37:46,599 --> 00:37:48,460
[SPEAKER_00] da on njemu pomogli da Trst ostane u Jugoslavi.

866
00:37:48,460 --> 00:37:49,760
[SPEAKER_00] A Staljin mu je rekao ne.

867
00:37:49,760 --> 00:37:51,500
[SPEAKER_00] I zato je Trst pripoji Italiji.

868
00:37:51,500 --> 00:37:53,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da je Tito bio tako moćan.

869
00:37:53,539 --> 00:37:56,400
[SPEAKER_00] Trst je bio do 1949. u Jugoslavi.

870
00:37:56,400 --> 00:38:00,119
[SPEAKER_00] Čak nogometni klub Trst je bio u Jugoslavijskoj ligi.

871
00:38:00,119 --> 00:38:01,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je Tito bio toliko moćan,

872
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:03,699
[SPEAKER_00] tako pametan, tako inteligentan,

873
00:38:03,699 --> 00:38:04,880
[SPEAKER_00] pa kako nije Trst zadržao.

874
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:06,820
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, Trst je već bio u sastavi Jugoslavi.

875
00:38:06,820 --> 00:38:09,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ono što je doista zapanjuje je

876
00:38:09,760 --> 00:38:11,320
[SPEAKER_01] da mi danas 2021.

877
00:38:11,320 --> 00:38:14,539
[SPEAKER_01] Da vi, evo, kroz civilno društvo,

878
00:38:14,539 --> 00:38:16,719
[SPEAKER_01] kroz ovu udrugu čiste član,

879
00:38:16,719 --> 00:38:18,679
[SPEAKER_01] kroz ukonačno financiranje

880
00:38:18,679 --> 00:38:21,239
[SPEAKER_01] od strane Australije,

881
00:38:21,239 --> 00:38:24,800
[SPEAKER_01] od gospodina Marka Franovića,

882
00:38:24,800 --> 00:38:26,480
[SPEAKER_01] od strane drugih ljudi

883
00:38:26,480 --> 00:38:28,880
[SPEAKER_01] koji žele da se istina kaže,

884
00:38:28,880 --> 00:38:30,280
[SPEAKER_01] istina, da se kaže istina

885
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:32,739
[SPEAKER_01] o tome što se događalo u Hrvatskoj

886
00:38:32,739 --> 00:38:34,500
[SPEAKER_01] za vrijeme rata,

887
00:38:34,500 --> 00:38:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] što se događalo poslije rata,

888
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:37,300
[SPEAKER_01] što se događalo u Jugoslaviji.

889
00:38:37,980 --> 00:38:39,440
[SPEAKER_01] Na kraju se sve ove aktivnosti

890
00:38:39,440 --> 00:38:41,099
[SPEAKER_01] istraživačkog rada vašeg

891
00:38:41,099 --> 00:38:42,539
[SPEAKER_01] i publicističkog

892
00:38:42,539 --> 00:38:44,320
[SPEAKER_01] financiraju sami ljudi.

893
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:46,039
[SPEAKER_01] To je meni nevjerojatno.

894
00:38:46,039 --> 00:38:48,260
[SPEAKER_01] Da mi danas to još moramo dokazivati,

895
00:38:48,260 --> 00:38:48,820
[SPEAKER_01] 2021.

896
00:38:48,820 --> 00:38:50,860
[SPEAKER_01] Da nekom treba tumačiti

897
00:38:50,860 --> 00:38:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] da je taj sustav

898
00:38:52,539 --> 00:38:54,760
[SPEAKER_01] u Jugoslavenski bio totalitaran.

899
00:38:54,760 --> 00:38:56,079
[SPEAKER_01] Da je partija provodila

900
00:38:56,079 --> 00:38:58,519
[SPEAKER_01] totalitarizam.

901
00:38:58,719 --> 00:39:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kad gledajte u gospodina Franovića,

902
00:39:00,380 --> 00:39:02,059
[SPEAKER_00] on je pješke pobjegao iz Jugoslavije,

903
00:39:02,059 --> 00:39:02,639
[SPEAKER_00] ali nije on sam.

904
00:39:02,639 --> 00:39:05,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ima sad neki povjećari razmišljaju

905
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:06,139
[SPEAKER_00] da se početi baviti to.

906
00:39:06,139 --> 00:39:07,340
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedna tema, zanimljiva.

907
00:39:07,340 --> 00:39:09,599
[SPEAKER_00] Znači do 60-ih godina su granice Jugoslavije

908
00:39:09,599 --> 00:39:10,139
[SPEAKER_00] bila zatvorene.

909
00:39:10,139 --> 00:39:11,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi su bježali.

910
00:39:11,219 --> 00:39:12,199
[SPEAKER_00] To je takav blagostanje.

911
00:39:12,199 --> 00:39:13,880
[SPEAKER_00] Bila su bježali preko granica

912
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:14,260
[SPEAKER_00] željnih Bosnih.

913
00:39:14,260 --> 00:39:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] Preko mora.

914
00:39:15,039 --> 00:39:16,519
[SPEAKER_00] Bježali svakako.

915
00:39:16,519 --> 00:39:18,980
[SPEAKER_00] Preko 200 tisuća ljudi je bježali

916
00:39:18,980 --> 00:39:19,780
[SPEAKER_00] iz Jugoslavije.

917
00:39:19,780 --> 00:39:21,460
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo kako.

918
00:39:22,460 --> 00:39:23,840
[SPEAKER_00] I plaćali su vodiče.

919
00:39:23,840 --> 00:39:25,579
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, meni je pričala jedna žena iz Pavuća

920
00:39:25,579 --> 00:39:26,119
[SPEAKER_00] kad je bježala.

921
00:39:26,119 --> 00:39:28,079
[SPEAKER_00] Prvi put su bježali pa je neki pas našao

922
00:39:28,079 --> 00:39:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] pa su je vratili nazad u brod.

923
00:39:29,559 --> 00:39:31,619
[SPEAKER_00] Onda opet pokušala,

924
00:39:31,619 --> 00:39:32,699
[SPEAKER_00] iz drugih puta je uspjela

925
00:39:32,699 --> 00:39:34,199
[SPEAKER_00] i na kraju završila u Australiji

926
00:39:34,199 --> 00:39:35,059
[SPEAKER_00] i tako dalje.

927
00:39:35,059 --> 00:39:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] A njena cijela obitelj je na kraju

928
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] tragično završila u Jugoslaviji.

929
00:39:38,420 --> 00:39:39,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ona se jedina spasila

930
00:39:39,619 --> 00:39:40,920
[SPEAKER_00] i jedina ima obitelj

931
00:39:40,920 --> 00:39:42,480
[SPEAKER_00] zato što je pobjegla iz te Jugoslavije.

932
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:44,719
[SPEAKER_00] Znači Jugoslavije bila tamnica naroda.

933
00:39:46,280 --> 00:39:48,260
[SPEAKER_00] uništavale ljuska prava, ljuske slobode.

934
00:39:48,260 --> 00:39:48,719
[SPEAKER_01] I to je samo kraja.

935
00:39:48,719 --> 00:39:50,639
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, ono, meni kad pričaju ove gluposti

936
00:39:50,639 --> 00:39:53,260
[SPEAKER_01] o tome da je postao sustav mekšim.

937
00:39:53,260 --> 00:39:54,260
[SPEAKER_01] On je postao,

938
00:39:54,260 --> 00:39:56,940
[SPEAKER_01] taj sustav se prilagođavao

939
00:39:56,940 --> 00:39:57,900
[SPEAKER_01] vremenu u kojem je bio.

940
00:39:57,900 --> 00:39:59,079
[SPEAKER_01] A pa oni su do kraja

941
00:39:59,079 --> 00:40:00,219
[SPEAKER_01] su podizane optužnice,

942
00:40:00,219 --> 00:40:01,079
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi zatvarani

943
00:40:01,079 --> 00:40:03,659
[SPEAKER_01] do 80-ih godina,

944
00:40:03,659 --> 00:40:04,440
[SPEAKER_01] do 90-te,

945
00:40:04,440 --> 00:40:05,519
[SPEAKER_01] do kraja.

946
00:40:05,519 --> 00:40:07,699
[SPEAKER_01] Cijelo vrijeme je bila opresija.

947
00:40:07,699 --> 00:40:08,480
[SPEAKER_00] Pa dobro,

948
00:40:08,480 --> 00:40:09,699
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo živjeli,

949
00:40:09,699 --> 00:40:11,679
[SPEAKER_00] recimo nama je to možda teško shvatiti,

950
00:40:11,679 --> 00:40:12,420
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam ročno 62.

951
00:40:12,760 --> 00:40:14,079
[SPEAKER_00] i mi smo živjeli u tom sustavu,

952
00:40:14,079 --> 00:40:15,099
[SPEAKER_00] mi nismo drugo ni vidjeli.

953
00:40:15,099 --> 00:40:16,440
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da mi nismo ni znali

954
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:17,059
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je to loše.

955
00:40:17,059 --> 00:40:17,800
[SPEAKER_00] Tek poslije,

956
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:18,460
[SPEAKER_00] kad smo izaštivan,

957
00:40:18,460 --> 00:40:19,659
[SPEAKER_00] kad smo vidjeli kakva je sloboda

958
00:40:19,659 --> 00:40:21,880
[SPEAKER_00] na zapadu i tako dalje,

959
00:40:21,880 --> 00:40:22,619
[SPEAKER_00] onda smo vidjeli u stvari

960
00:40:22,619 --> 00:40:23,920
[SPEAKER_00] da je stvarno ta Jugoslavija

961
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:24,739
[SPEAKER_00] bila tamnica naroda.

962
00:40:24,739 --> 00:40:25,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ali meni je ovo,

963
00:40:25,500 --> 00:40:27,659
[SPEAKER_01] kad se ovo pitanje postavi,

964
00:40:27,659 --> 00:40:30,059
[SPEAKER_01] da li je Zagreb bio oslobođen,

965
00:40:30,059 --> 00:40:32,739
[SPEAKER_01] oslobođen ili okupiran,

966
00:40:32,739 --> 00:40:35,880
[SPEAKER_01] na to pitanje su Poljaci odgovorili

967
00:40:35,880 --> 00:40:38,199
[SPEAKER_01] što se dogodilo kada su Rusi,

968
00:40:38,199 --> 00:40:40,239
[SPEAKER_01] kada su komunisti ušli u Poljsku,

969
00:40:40,300 --> 00:40:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] kada su komunisti ušli u Češku.

970
00:40:42,000 --> 00:40:42,920
[SPEAKER_00] To je nova okupacija.

971
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:43,900
[SPEAKER_01] To je nova okupacija.

972
00:40:43,900 --> 00:40:46,260
[SPEAKER_01] Kad su komunisti ušli u Mađarsku,

973
00:40:46,260 --> 00:40:47,159
[SPEAKER_01] to je nova okupacija.

974
00:40:47,159 --> 00:40:48,579
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, sve države,

975
00:40:48,579 --> 00:40:52,320
[SPEAKER_01] ove koje su bili pod komunističkom okupacijom,

976
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:56,179
[SPEAKER_01] su jasno to priznale i rekle.

977
00:40:56,179 --> 00:40:58,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ali u Hrvatskoj vi imate,

978
00:40:58,420 --> 00:41:02,059
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, još uvijek političke kaste

979
00:41:02,059 --> 00:41:05,340
[SPEAKER_01] i ljude koji su ušli u kulturu,

980
00:41:05,340 --> 00:41:06,039
[SPEAKER_01] u medije,

981
00:41:06,039 --> 00:41:07,679
[SPEAKER_01] koji vama tvrde suprotno.

982
00:41:07,800 --> 00:41:10,679
[SPEAKER_01] i koji pokušavaju one koji daju odgovor

983
00:41:10,679 --> 00:41:12,820
[SPEAKER_01] na pitanje da je Zagreb bio okupiran

984
00:41:12,820 --> 00:41:14,260
[SPEAKER_01] drugom vojskom,

985
00:41:14,260 --> 00:41:15,920
[SPEAKER_01] također totalitarnom obtužiti

986
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:18,019
[SPEAKER_01] da su filofašisti.

987
00:41:18,019 --> 00:41:19,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to je fakat nevjerojatno.

988
00:41:19,960 --> 00:41:21,739
[SPEAKER_00] Pa dobro, mi možemo postaviti drugo pitanje.

989
00:41:21,739 --> 00:41:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] Može li Jugoslavija,

990
00:41:22,500 --> 00:41:24,599
[SPEAKER_00] može li Srpska vojska oslobodi Đakova?

991
00:41:24,599 --> 00:41:27,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ako može 21. Srpska oslobodi Đakova,

992
00:41:27,119 --> 00:41:28,860
[SPEAKER_00] onda Novosadski korpus je oslobodio Vukov.

993
00:41:28,860 --> 00:41:31,760
[SPEAKER_00] Iz teritorika, imate pravo.

994
00:41:31,760 --> 00:41:34,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je to tako kako oni govore.

995
00:41:34,139 --> 00:41:37,980
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, mi možemo govoriti recimo da je Jugoslavija ostala,

996
00:41:37,980 --> 00:41:39,480
[SPEAKER_00] da je Jugoslavija ostala kao država,

997
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:41,980
[SPEAKER_00] onda bi mogli razgovarati da je nešto oslobođeno.

998
00:41:41,980 --> 00:41:43,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ali budući da Jugoslavije nema,

999
00:41:43,679 --> 00:41:44,519
[SPEAKER_00] ona se raspala,

1000
00:41:44,519 --> 00:41:46,679
[SPEAKER_00] ona je sama sebe uništila,

1001
00:41:46,679 --> 00:41:47,820
[SPEAKER_00] ona nije bila prirodna,

1002
00:41:47,820 --> 00:41:49,559
[SPEAKER_00] ona nije bila volja naroda.

1003
00:41:49,559 --> 00:41:51,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ja gledam kad kod nas isto govore

1004
00:41:51,280 --> 00:41:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] na temelju Avnoja i Zavnoha.

1005
00:41:53,000 --> 00:41:54,260
[SPEAKER_00] Što je to Avnoja i Zavnoha?

1006
00:41:54,260 --> 00:41:56,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kakav je, kakva je to legitimno tijelo?

1007
00:41:56,900 --> 00:42:00,840
[SPEAKER_00] To su delegati koji niko nije izabro.

1008
00:42:00,840 --> 00:42:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] Možemo se sad nas,

1009
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:03,019
[SPEAKER_00] evo skupi se nas deset,

1010
00:42:03,019 --> 00:42:05,320
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo antikomunistička stranka,

1011
00:42:05,320 --> 00:42:07,659
[SPEAKER_00] mi tvrdimo da Hrvatska je antikomunistička država

1012
00:42:07,659 --> 00:42:08,559
[SPEAKER_00] i sve rušimo sada.

1013
00:42:08,559 --> 00:42:09,559
[SPEAKER_00] I kažemo Hrvatska,

1014
00:42:09,559 --> 00:42:10,920
[SPEAKER_00] a nas deset se naslobi jer ti.

1015
00:42:10,920 --> 00:42:11,940
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ko je nas izabro?

1016
00:42:11,940 --> 00:42:13,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je izabro te delegate?

1017
00:42:13,480 --> 00:42:15,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam gledao recimo u Zavnohu,

1018
00:42:15,460 --> 00:42:17,099
[SPEAKER_00] baš na malo gledajte original dokumente,

1019
00:42:17,099 --> 00:42:19,480
[SPEAKER_00] delegati Zavnoha su bili Sremske Mitrovice.

1020
00:42:19,480 --> 00:42:21,760
[SPEAKER_00] Ako je delegat Zavnoha iz Sremske Mitrovice,

1021
00:42:21,760 --> 00:42:23,679
[SPEAKER_00] kako onda Sremska Mitrovica je ni u Hrvatskoj?

1022
00:42:23,679 --> 00:42:27,059
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ti svi njihovi dokumenti,

1023
00:42:27,059 --> 00:42:28,300
[SPEAKER_00] te sve njihove odluke,

1024
00:42:28,300 --> 00:42:30,440
[SPEAKER_00] to je sve nelegalno,

1025
00:42:30,440 --> 00:42:32,019
[SPEAKER_00] nedemokratski

1026
00:42:32,019 --> 00:42:34,980
[SPEAKER_00] i to nije volja naroda izmeđa ostalog.

1027
00:42:34,980 --> 00:42:36,579
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da, jednopartijski sustav.

1028
00:42:36,579 --> 00:42:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna jedna partija je bila,

1029
00:42:39,599 --> 00:42:41,119
[SPEAKER_01] o čem što još treba objasniti?

1030
00:42:41,119 --> 00:42:41,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam gledao,

1031
00:42:41,940 --> 00:42:43,099
[SPEAKER_00] evo kad to spominjem,

1032
00:42:43,099 --> 00:42:44,760
[SPEAKER_00] koji je bio recimo u Saboru NDH,

1033
00:42:44,880 --> 00:42:47,119
[SPEAKER_00] obnovljen 1942. godine,

1034
00:42:47,119 --> 00:42:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] ali gledam šta su oni radili.

1035
00:42:48,480 --> 00:42:49,059
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su gledali,

1036
00:42:49,059 --> 00:42:51,139
[SPEAKER_00] svi zastupnike HSS-a su tražili,

1037
00:42:51,139 --> 00:42:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] koji su izabrani 1939.

1038
00:42:52,539 --> 00:42:54,860
[SPEAKER_00] da bi imali nekakav legitimitet.

1039
00:42:54,860 --> 00:42:56,699
[SPEAKER_00] Znači oni koji su izabrani na izborima,

1040
00:42:56,699 --> 00:42:59,780
[SPEAKER_00] na listama neke druge stranke,

1041
00:42:59,780 --> 00:43:00,920
[SPEAKER_00] a to imamo i sad u Saboru,

1042
00:43:00,920 --> 00:43:02,280
[SPEAKER_00] čovjek uđe u nekoj drugoj stranci,

1043
00:43:02,280 --> 00:43:04,420
[SPEAKER_00] pa da ne znam glas onome,

1044
00:43:04,420 --> 00:43:05,300
[SPEAKER_00] ko je neko drugačiji.

1045
00:43:05,300 --> 00:43:06,280
[SPEAKER_00] Varaju i sada,

1046
00:43:06,280 --> 00:43:07,119
[SPEAKER_00] kao što su i prijateljali.

1047
00:43:07,119 --> 00:43:08,039
[SPEAKER_00] A to je 1942. bilo.

1048
00:43:08,039 --> 00:43:09,900
[SPEAKER_00] Znači svi koji su 1942.

1049
00:43:09,900 --> 00:43:11,820
[SPEAKER_00] izabrani na listi HSS-a,

1050
00:43:12,059 --> 00:43:14,059
[SPEAKER_00] poslije su većina pristupili

1051
00:43:14,059 --> 00:43:14,900
[SPEAKER_00] u Ustaškom pokretu

1052
00:43:14,900 --> 00:43:17,099
[SPEAKER_00] i oni su davali nekakav legitimitet saboru.

1053
00:43:17,099 --> 00:43:19,159
[SPEAKER_00] A kakav legitimitet ima Zavnoho?

1054
00:43:19,159 --> 00:43:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] Nemani, tamo našli se ne znam nijav,

1055
00:43:20,900 --> 00:43:21,599
[SPEAKER_00] ili u jajcu.

1056
00:43:21,599 --> 00:43:23,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je došao u jajcu

1057
00:43:23,019 --> 00:43:24,719
[SPEAKER_00] i ko ga tamo predstavlja?

1058
00:43:24,719 --> 00:43:25,820
[SPEAKER_00] I onda mi kažemo,

1059
00:43:25,820 --> 00:43:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] po Ustavu sada Republike Hrvatske,

1060
00:43:28,000 --> 00:43:29,340
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo nastavili na Zavnohova.

1061
00:43:29,340 --> 00:43:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je Zavnoho?

1062
00:43:29,960 --> 00:43:31,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ko predstavlja Zavnoho?

1063
00:43:31,280 --> 00:43:32,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je to? Što je to?

1064
00:43:32,559 --> 00:43:35,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ali i ta, s druge strane,

1065
00:43:35,159 --> 00:43:37,420
[SPEAKER_01] ovi ti zločini koje vi rasvjetljavate

1066
00:43:37,420 --> 00:43:39,099
[SPEAKER_01] i koje stalno dižete u javnost,

1067
00:43:39,099 --> 00:43:40,280
[SPEAKER_01] doista je to potrebno.

1068
00:43:40,280 --> 00:43:43,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam, prvi put kad sam otišla na Blajburg,

1069
00:43:43,360 --> 00:43:48,119
[SPEAKER_01] mene je šokirala razlika

1070
00:43:48,119 --> 00:43:51,820
[SPEAKER_01] u atmosferi koja vlada na Blajburgu

1071
00:43:51,820 --> 00:43:54,960
[SPEAKER_01] u odnosu na ono kako mediji to prikazuju,

1072
00:43:54,960 --> 00:43:56,159
[SPEAKER_01] kako su prikaziva.

1073
00:43:56,480 --> 00:43:59,079
[SPEAKER_01] U stvari, mene tako me se dojmila

1074
00:43:59,079 --> 00:44:00,679
[SPEAKER_01] ta tuga ogromna,

1075
00:44:00,679 --> 00:44:02,179
[SPEAKER_01] tih svih ljudi koji su bili.

1076
00:44:02,179 --> 00:44:04,619
[SPEAKER_01] To su sve članovi, obitelji, ljudi

1077
00:44:04,619 --> 00:44:06,239
[SPEAKER_01] koji su u miru,

1078
00:44:06,239 --> 00:44:08,260
[SPEAKER_01] kad je rad bio gotov,

1079
00:44:08,260 --> 00:44:10,019
[SPEAKER_01] ubijeni iz mržnje,

1080
00:44:10,019 --> 00:44:11,679
[SPEAKER_01] zato što su Hrvati,

1081
00:44:11,679 --> 00:44:14,579
[SPEAKER_01] ubijeni žene, djeca, muškati.

1082
00:44:14,579 --> 00:44:16,460
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, taj skup na Blajbru,

1083
00:44:16,460 --> 00:44:18,079
[SPEAKER_01] kad dođeš tamo,

1084
00:44:18,079 --> 00:44:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] to nije bila nikakvo veličanje,

1085
00:44:20,079 --> 00:44:21,820
[SPEAKER_01] nikakvog ustaškog režima.

1086
00:44:21,820 --> 00:44:23,340
[SPEAKER_01] To je jedan ogromna rana

1087
00:44:23,340 --> 00:44:24,400
[SPEAKER_01] hrvatskog naroda.

1088
00:44:24,400 --> 00:44:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, prema informacijama,

1089
00:44:26,480 --> 00:44:27,699
[SPEAKER_01] koje daju demografi,

1090
00:44:27,699 --> 00:44:30,739
[SPEAKER_01] obijeno je preko 300 tisuća ljudi

1091
00:44:30,739 --> 00:44:31,760
[SPEAKER_01] u tom razdoblju.

1092
00:44:31,760 --> 00:44:33,739
[SPEAKER_01] Prema tome, mi danas osjećamo

1093
00:44:33,739 --> 00:44:34,900
[SPEAKER_01] gubitak svih tih ljudi.

1094
00:44:34,900 --> 00:44:36,179
[SPEAKER_00] Na Blajbru sam ješao gotovo

1095
00:44:36,179 --> 00:44:37,400
[SPEAKER_00] svake godine u autobusu,

1096
00:44:37,400 --> 00:44:38,099
[SPEAKER_00] po 50 ljudi.

1097
00:44:38,099 --> 00:44:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] Znate kakav je to osjećao u autobusu?

1098
00:44:40,159 --> 00:44:41,300
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi kad su izlazili

1099
00:44:41,300 --> 00:44:42,679
[SPEAKER_00] sadašnje Hrvatske na Blajbru

1100
00:44:42,679 --> 00:44:44,360
[SPEAKER_00] osjećali su kao da izlaze na slobodnu.

1101
00:44:44,360 --> 00:44:45,920
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ni sadašnja Hrvatska

1102
00:44:45,920 --> 00:44:47,300
[SPEAKER_00] se ne osjeća kao slobodna država

1103
00:44:47,300 --> 00:44:48,559
[SPEAKER_00] i oni kad hoće pričati

1104
00:44:48,559 --> 00:44:49,760
[SPEAKER_00] o svom stricu u Ustaši,

1105
00:44:56,480 --> 00:44:57,960
[SPEAKER_00] muze autobusu, već liju

1106
00:44:57,960 --> 00:44:59,340
[SPEAKER_00] i onda kad dođu na taj Blajbru

1107
00:44:59,340 --> 00:45:01,539
[SPEAKER_00] oni smatraju kao da je to Međugorje,

1108
00:45:01,539 --> 00:45:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] kao da se tu gospa ukazala,

1109
00:45:03,000 --> 00:45:05,219
[SPEAKER_00] kao da je tu sloboda mišljenja,

1110
00:45:05,219 --> 00:45:06,820
[SPEAKER_00] da će ponovo se sresti

1111
00:45:06,820 --> 00:45:07,900
[SPEAKER_00] sa svojim bivšim mrtvima.

1112
00:45:07,900 --> 00:45:08,860
[SPEAKER_00] Da mogu reći istinu, tako je.

1113
00:45:08,860 --> 00:45:11,079
[SPEAKER_01] Da njihovi mrtvi, veliki mrtvi,

1114
00:45:11,079 --> 00:45:12,380
[SPEAKER_01] nisu zločinci.

1115
00:45:12,380 --> 00:45:12,840
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

1116
00:45:12,840 --> 00:45:14,380
[SPEAKER_01] A to je ono što uporno dalje

1117
00:45:14,380 --> 00:45:15,699
[SPEAKER_01] se pokušava reći da svi

1118
00:45:15,699 --> 00:45:17,599
[SPEAKER_01] koji su ubijeni su bili zločinci.

1119
00:45:17,599 --> 00:45:19,139
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da su i bili zločinci,

1120
00:45:19,139 --> 00:45:20,059
[SPEAKER_01] pa ne može ga ubijati

1121
00:45:20,059 --> 00:45:21,460
[SPEAKER_01] po cesti i muđiti.

1122
00:45:21,460 --> 00:45:22,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ali nisu bili.

1123
00:45:22,599 --> 00:45:23,260
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nisu bili.

1124
00:45:23,260 --> 00:45:24,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ali druga stvar je

1125
00:45:24,820 --> 00:45:26,699
[SPEAKER_01] koju ste vi isto tako istraživali,

1126
00:45:26,699 --> 00:45:28,059
[SPEAKER_01] za koju bih vas molila

1127
00:45:28,059 --> 00:45:29,500
[SPEAKER_01] da nam nešto barem kažete,

1128
00:45:29,500 --> 00:45:31,820
[SPEAKER_01] jer ja nisam doista to čula

1129
00:45:31,820 --> 00:45:32,539
[SPEAKER_01] na jednom mjestu,

1130
00:45:32,539 --> 00:45:35,360
[SPEAKER_01] tako jasno kako ste vi to znate predstaviti,

1131
00:45:35,360 --> 00:45:37,360
[SPEAKER_01] su logori koje su komunisti,

1132
00:45:37,360 --> 00:45:39,900
[SPEAKER_01] koje je Jugoslavenska armija

1133
00:45:39,900 --> 00:45:41,360
[SPEAKER_01] otvarala za Volksdeutsere.

1134
00:45:41,360 --> 00:45:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedna velika tragedija.

1135
00:45:44,460 --> 00:45:45,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ali možemo razgovarati,

1136
00:45:45,840 --> 00:45:47,579
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj samo baš kad gledamo te dokumente,

1137
00:45:47,579 --> 00:45:49,360
[SPEAKER_00] znači nakon 45. cijela Jugoslavija

1138
00:45:49,360 --> 00:45:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] je bila logor.

1139
00:45:50,059 --> 00:45:51,460
[SPEAKER_00] Oni kažu bio logor Jasenovac.

1140
00:45:51,460 --> 00:45:53,760
[SPEAKER_00] Jasenovac je radio i nakon 45.

1141
00:45:53,760 --> 00:45:54,679
[SPEAKER_00] Evo dokumenti,

1142
00:45:54,679 --> 00:45:55,360
[SPEAKER_00] ima ja ko će,

1143
00:45:55,360 --> 00:45:56,380
[SPEAKER_00] ja ću mu poslati.

1144
00:45:56,380 --> 00:45:57,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ima jedan dokument

1145
00:45:57,360 --> 00:45:59,219
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je pobjeglo sedam logoraša iz logora.

1146
00:45:59,219 --> 00:46:01,059
[SPEAKER_00] I njih pita tužitelj,

1147
00:46:01,059 --> 00:46:02,960
[SPEAKER_00] taj tužitelj u SISK-u,

1148
00:46:02,960 --> 00:46:05,099
[SPEAKER_00] zašto ste pobjegli iz logora Jasenovac?

1149
00:46:05,099 --> 00:46:07,360
[SPEAKER_00] Kako su oni mogli pobjegli iz logora Jasenovac

1150
00:46:07,360 --> 00:46:08,280
[SPEAKER_00] ako logor nije postojao?

1151
00:46:08,280 --> 00:46:09,380
[SPEAKER_00] To je 46. godina.

1152
00:46:09,380 --> 00:46:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] Znači imaju dokumenti.

1153
00:46:10,980 --> 00:46:13,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ja vjerujem da će se ti dokumenti još naći.

1154
00:46:13,380 --> 00:46:15,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ali što se tiče recimo Volksdeutsera...

1155
00:46:15,880 --> 00:46:17,480
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to su Njemci koji su...

1156
00:46:17,480 --> 00:46:19,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, oni su bili nacionalna manjina.

1157
00:46:19,699 --> 00:46:21,920
[SPEAKER_01] Samo da kažemo za oni koji možda ne znaju.

1158
00:46:21,920 --> 00:46:24,880
[SPEAKER_01] Pripadnici Njemačke nacionalne manjine

1159
00:46:24,880 --> 00:46:26,739
[SPEAKER_01] koji su živjeli u Hrvatskoj autori...

1160
00:46:26,739 --> 00:46:28,179
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, stanovništvu koje je živjelo

1161
00:46:28,179 --> 00:46:29,599
[SPEAKER_01] prije drugog svjetskog rata.

1162
00:46:29,599 --> 00:46:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

1163
00:46:30,380 --> 00:46:33,099
[SPEAKER_00] Jer oni su bili krivi samo zato što su Njemci.

1164
00:46:33,099 --> 00:46:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] Njemci, da.

1165
00:46:33,420 --> 00:46:34,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kao recimo što su ljudi

1166
00:46:34,880 --> 00:46:36,980
[SPEAKER_00] koji su do 14. bili krivi zato što su bili Romi

1167
00:46:36,980 --> 00:46:38,119
[SPEAKER_00] ili zato što su bili Židovi.

1168
00:46:38,119 --> 00:46:40,360
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su bili krivi samo zato što su Njemci.

1169
00:46:40,739 --> 00:46:41,579
[SPEAKER_00] I za njih su...

1170
00:46:41,579 --> 00:46:43,460
[SPEAKER_00] Čak recimo u Đakovu sabirni logor,

1171
00:46:43,460 --> 00:46:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] u Đakovu koji je bio za židove,

1172
00:46:44,599 --> 00:46:45,699
[SPEAKER_00] bio je na kraju i za Njemce.

1173
00:46:45,699 --> 00:46:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] Sabirni.

1174
00:46:46,380 --> 00:46:48,659
[SPEAKER_00] I odatle su ih vodili u Krndiju i dalje.

1175
00:46:48,659 --> 00:46:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da čak i logori su znali biti isti.

1176
00:46:50,900 --> 00:46:53,840
[SPEAKER_00] Što se tiče Njemaca,

1177
00:46:53,840 --> 00:46:55,059
[SPEAKER_00] znači na području Slavonije,

1178
00:46:55,059 --> 00:46:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] tamo, najviše logora tamo i bilo,

1179
00:46:57,159 --> 00:46:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] znači to je bilo Krndijako.

1180
00:46:58,440 --> 00:47:00,559
[SPEAKER_00] Od Đakova, Valpovo, Josipovac

1181
00:47:00,559 --> 00:47:03,019
[SPEAKER_00] i vamo velika pisanica kod Bjelovara.

1182
00:47:03,019 --> 00:47:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] Znači na prostoru u Gostavi žirlo je

1183
00:47:05,380 --> 00:47:06,800
[SPEAKER_00] oko 500 tisuća Njemaca.

1184
00:47:06,920 --> 00:47:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] tada se može da izjašnjava u Đakovu možda 10-15 ljudi.

1185
00:47:10,000 --> 00:47:11,579
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da...

1186
00:47:11,579 --> 00:47:15,260
[SPEAKER_00] Očistili su cijeli taj prostor od Njemaca.

1187
00:47:15,260 --> 00:47:16,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ali što je još zanimljivo,

1188
00:47:16,380 --> 00:47:18,639
[SPEAKER_00] većina tih Njemaca je odvežena

1189
00:47:18,639 --> 00:47:20,300
[SPEAKER_00] u sadašnji prostor Donjecka.

1190
00:47:20,300 --> 00:47:21,780
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo čak imao, znači,

1191
00:47:21,780 --> 00:47:23,420
[SPEAKER_00] folk zločera s potvora bivše Jugoslave,

1192
00:47:23,420 --> 00:47:24,679
[SPEAKER_00] tamo su bili nekakvi rudnici,

1193
00:47:24,679 --> 00:47:25,980
[SPEAKER_00] tako da su Njemci, znači,

1194
00:47:25,980 --> 00:47:27,280
[SPEAKER_00] iz ovih prostora neki završili,

1195
00:47:27,280 --> 00:47:29,019
[SPEAKER_00] znači, na prostoru gdje je sada rat.

1196
00:47:29,019 --> 00:47:30,679
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, taj prostor...

1197
00:47:30,679 --> 00:47:32,820
[SPEAKER_01] Vi ste rekli da su prema dokumentima

1198
00:47:32,820 --> 00:47:33,659
[SPEAKER_01] koje ste istraživali,

1199
00:47:33,659 --> 00:47:36,619
[SPEAKER_01] veliki dio bila u stvari žene i djeca

1200
00:47:36,619 --> 00:47:37,079
[SPEAKER_01] u tim logorima.

1201
00:47:37,079 --> 00:47:37,960
[SPEAKER_00] 90%.

1202
00:47:37,960 --> 00:47:39,760
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, recimo, jer što se dogodilo,

1203
00:47:39,760 --> 00:47:41,820
[SPEAKER_00] kao i među Hrvatima i među svima ostalima,

1204
00:47:41,820 --> 00:47:43,420
[SPEAKER_00] većina muških ljudi je poginula,

1205
00:47:43,420 --> 00:47:44,340
[SPEAKER_00] što sliče njema.

1206
00:47:44,340 --> 00:47:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] Sa ostale su žene i djeca.

1207
00:47:45,460 --> 00:47:48,199
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, imate logor Gakovo kod ovoga,

1208
00:47:48,199 --> 00:47:49,820
[SPEAKER_00] kak se zove, Gakovo kod Sombora.

1209
00:47:49,820 --> 00:47:51,099
[SPEAKER_00] To je katastrofa.

1210
00:47:51,099 --> 00:47:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Taj logor je, znači,

1211
00:47:52,000 --> 00:47:54,300
[SPEAKER_00] radio od 1945. do 1949. godine.

1212
00:47:54,699 --> 00:47:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam pokušao doći do svih imena.

1213
00:47:56,539 --> 00:47:57,780
[SPEAKER_00] Bio sam u arhivu u Somboru

1214
00:47:57,780 --> 00:47:58,780
[SPEAKER_00] i tamo u njihovom.

1215
00:47:58,780 --> 00:48:03,219
[SPEAKER_00] Oni posjeduju nekdje oko 12.000 imena

1216
00:48:03,219 --> 00:48:04,239
[SPEAKER_00] umrli žena i djece.

1217
00:48:04,239 --> 00:48:05,460
[SPEAKER_00] 12.000.

1218
00:48:05,460 --> 00:48:06,159
[SPEAKER_00] Straž.

1219
00:48:06,159 --> 00:48:08,460
[SPEAKER_00] To je, znači, pojmenični popis.

1220
00:48:08,460 --> 00:48:10,880
[SPEAKER_00] Jer, ovaj, vlasti u to vrijeme su popisili.

1221
00:48:10,880 --> 00:48:12,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam vidio te knjige kako izgledaju.

1222
00:48:12,519 --> 00:48:16,219
[SPEAKER_00] I, ovaj, znači, oko 12.000 žena i djece.

1223
00:48:16,219 --> 00:48:19,800
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, recimo, Vladimir Galgir je dosta to opisao

1224
00:48:19,800 --> 00:48:21,760
[SPEAKER_00] i imaju, recimo, pisma iz Krndije

1225
00:48:21,760 --> 00:48:23,079
[SPEAKER_00] od gospođe Kneblu.

1226
00:48:23,079 --> 00:48:25,099
[SPEAKER_00] Mogu navesti primjer, evo, iz Žakova.

1227
00:48:25,099 --> 00:48:27,780
[SPEAKER_00] Kad sam ja to radio, jedna žena,

1228
00:48:27,780 --> 00:48:30,219
[SPEAKER_00] prezime, ona je uvijek rekla da ne kažem,

1229
00:48:30,219 --> 00:48:31,699
[SPEAKER_00] ona je sad umrla, ali neću joj reći prezime.

1230
00:48:31,699 --> 00:48:33,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ona priča kako je njoj bilo.

1231
00:48:33,639 --> 00:48:35,320
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, njenog tatu kad su ušli,

1232
00:48:35,320 --> 00:48:36,519
[SPEAKER_00] kao njemca, odmah su ubili.

1233
00:48:36,519 --> 00:48:37,840
[SPEAKER_00] Mamu i njenog...

1234
00:48:37,840 --> 00:48:39,480
[SPEAKER_00] Partizani su, dakle, partizani.

1235
00:48:39,480 --> 00:48:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] Jugoslavijska vojca je ubila.

1236
00:48:40,619 --> 00:48:41,239
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ulaze, goslavijska.

1237
00:48:41,239 --> 00:48:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ulaze, onda sve njemce hapse.

1238
00:48:43,039 --> 00:48:43,880
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, nema tu.

1239
00:48:44,039 --> 00:48:44,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si njemac, kriv si.

1240
00:48:44,960 --> 00:48:47,619
[SPEAKER_00] Nema tu, samo je si njemac ili kao što je prije bilo

1241
00:48:47,619 --> 00:48:48,739
[SPEAKER_00] za židove i za rome.

1242
00:48:48,739 --> 00:48:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] Ako si židov, kriv si.

1243
00:48:50,659 --> 00:48:52,440
[SPEAKER_00] A ovdje, ako si njemac, kriv si.

1244
00:48:52,440 --> 00:48:55,699
[SPEAKER_00] E sad, kad gledamo sa osobne tragedije,

1245
00:48:55,699 --> 00:48:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] to je možda pitanje za sociologe i psihologe.

1246
00:48:58,519 --> 00:49:00,380
[SPEAKER_00] Ali evo, ja ću sad govoriti sa činjenično što je bilo.

1247
00:49:00,380 --> 00:49:02,840
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, oni dolaze, tatu ubiju odmah, kaže,

1248
00:49:02,840 --> 00:49:06,760
[SPEAKER_00] a mama je bila trudna i u visokom stupnju trudnoće.

1249
00:49:06,760 --> 00:49:08,079
[SPEAKER_00] I od dolazi u logor Krndija.

1250
00:49:08,079 --> 00:49:09,739
[SPEAKER_00] I ona meni priča, ona se sjeća.

1251
00:49:10,039 --> 00:49:11,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ona se sjeća da je mama rađala.

1252
00:49:11,440 --> 00:49:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] I da li je djete živo, ona se ne sjeća.

1253
00:49:13,599 --> 00:49:16,480
[SPEAKER_00] Ali uglavnom, više ni vidila ni mamu, ni tog brata.

1254
00:49:16,480 --> 00:49:19,559
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže, nakon par dana, partizani u nekakvom kamionu

1255
00:49:19,559 --> 00:49:21,039
[SPEAKER_00] nju istovaraju pre njihovu kuću.

1256
00:49:21,039 --> 00:49:23,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ona dolazi u kuću, partizani već zauzeli kuću.

1257
00:49:23,719 --> 00:49:27,079
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ona je imala u to vrijeme možda 7-8 godina ili 9,

1258
00:49:27,079 --> 00:49:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] a brat je imao 4-5-6 godina.

1259
00:49:30,380 --> 00:49:32,019
[SPEAKER_00] I oni njih istjeraju van.

1260
00:49:32,019 --> 00:49:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] I oni hodaju po džaku u policu, to je Selačka ulica.

1261
00:49:35,059 --> 00:49:36,719
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, hodaju, svi se boje uzeti.

1262
00:49:36,719 --> 00:49:38,960
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako uzmu, onda će biti krivi, pomažu...

1263
00:49:38,960 --> 00:49:42,820
[SPEAKER_01] Da pomažu, ne pomažu, pa šiste pomažu, naciste pomažu.

1264
00:49:42,820 --> 00:49:45,739
[SPEAKER_00] A djete od 6-7 godina.

1265
00:49:45,739 --> 00:49:49,739
[SPEAKER_00] I onda na kraju, meni pričaju, ja tamo to gledao,

1266
00:49:49,739 --> 00:49:51,679
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, čovjeka, za ne kažem, plako i kaže,

1267
00:49:51,679 --> 00:49:52,960
[SPEAKER_00] ja ne mogu išaj, ću uzeti u djese.

1268
00:49:52,960 --> 00:49:55,679
[SPEAKER_00] I on njih uzao i spasio i tako da...

1269
00:49:55,679 --> 00:49:56,980
[SPEAKER_00] To su, kažem, to su ovaj...

1270
00:49:56,980 --> 00:49:58,300
[SPEAKER_00] Straš, tko je zlo.

1271
00:49:58,300 --> 00:49:59,559
[SPEAKER_00] To priča, to ti dođe da plaćaš.

1272
00:49:59,559 --> 00:50:00,679
[SPEAKER_00] Pa plaćaš, pa da.

1273
00:50:00,739 --> 00:50:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] I onda poslije ona govorila, kada su ih htjeli uzeti,

1274
00:50:03,000 --> 00:50:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, onda su uvijek htjeli odvojiti mene i brata,

1275
00:50:04,559 --> 00:50:06,260
[SPEAKER_00] kaže, ja uvijek njega, uvijek sam njega držala

1276
00:50:06,260 --> 00:50:07,099
[SPEAKER_00] i nisam ga htjela dati.

1277
00:50:07,099 --> 00:50:08,059
[SPEAKER_01] Dati od sebe.

1278
00:50:08,059 --> 00:50:11,280
[SPEAKER_01] I što su oni pretrpili, onda su ih još uvjeravali

1279
00:50:11,280 --> 00:50:13,519
[SPEAKER_01] 45 godina kak je to super vlasti,

1280
00:50:13,519 --> 00:50:15,019
[SPEAKER_01] kako to trebaju slaviti, to vrijeme.

1281
00:50:15,019 --> 00:50:16,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ja, ta žena je cijeli život bila žena

1282
00:50:16,780 --> 00:50:19,039
[SPEAKER_00] kao drugog reda.

1283
00:50:19,039 --> 00:50:20,860
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, u školi je bila žena drugog reda.

1284
00:50:20,860 --> 00:50:22,739
[SPEAKER_00] Onda, ovaj, ma do smrti,

1285
00:50:22,739 --> 00:50:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] ona je takav težak život imala.

1286
00:50:24,619 --> 00:50:26,780
[SPEAKER_00] To je teško zavijet.

1287
00:50:26,780 --> 00:50:28,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, evo, možemo drugi primjer navesti.

1288
00:50:28,219 --> 00:50:31,800
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, srpske novine vreme imaju kolumne od Ivana Ivanja.

1289
00:50:31,800 --> 00:50:34,300
[SPEAKER_00] On je židov iz Rljanina,

1290
00:50:34,300 --> 00:50:35,559
[SPEAKER_00] koji je bio u Auschwitzu.

1291
00:50:35,559 --> 00:50:37,039
[SPEAKER_00] I on u jednoj svojej kolumni piše,

1292
00:50:37,039 --> 00:50:39,159
[SPEAKER_00] mi se zove kolumne da se ubijalo, ubijalo se,

1293
00:50:39,159 --> 00:50:40,739
[SPEAKER_00] gdje on baš priča sa partizanima.

1294
00:50:40,739 --> 00:50:44,159
[SPEAKER_00] On pita, kako ste vi ubijali u logorima za Njemce?

1295
00:50:44,159 --> 00:50:46,239
[SPEAKER_00] I onda on uspoređuje sa logorima gdje on bio.

1296
00:50:46,239 --> 00:50:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] On je bio u Auschwitzu.

1297
00:50:47,519 --> 00:50:49,219
[SPEAKER_00] I onda jedna njegova tajnica, koja je bila,

1298
00:50:52,739 --> 00:50:54,480
[SPEAKER_00] i onda ona priča kako je bilo u njoj u Gakovu.

1299
00:50:54,480 --> 00:50:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] Onda ona kaže kako je to bilo da nisu dobivali hranu,

1300
00:50:58,039 --> 00:51:00,059
[SPEAKER_00] nije bilo prozora vrata, ništa.

1301
00:51:00,059 --> 00:51:02,579
[SPEAKER_00] Oni su umirali i od gladi u logoru i od hladnoće.

1302
00:51:02,579 --> 00:51:05,019
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kaže, sjeća se kad bi bacali ljude na,

1303
00:51:05,019 --> 00:51:07,159
[SPEAKER_00] kako se zove, na kola i vozili ih.

1304
00:51:07,159 --> 00:51:08,639
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kad bi baci u tu veliku jamu,

1305
00:51:08,639 --> 00:51:10,039
[SPEAKER_00] onda dođu štakori, jedu te ljude,

1306
00:51:10,039 --> 00:51:12,739
[SPEAKER_00] takvo grobište imao u džaku.

1307
00:51:12,739 --> 00:51:14,159
[SPEAKER_00] To su mi još neki govorili.

1308
00:51:14,159 --> 00:51:17,780
[SPEAKER_00] I onda baš on postavlja pitanje

1309
00:51:17,780 --> 00:51:20,380
[SPEAKER_00] da li je bilo teže njima kad su ubijeni odmah ciklonom B

1310
00:51:20,380 --> 00:51:24,159
[SPEAKER_00] ili ovi što su umirali danima od gladi, bolesti i tako dalje,

1311
00:51:24,159 --> 00:51:25,360
[SPEAKER_00] bez ikakve brige.

1312
00:51:25,360 --> 00:51:27,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, možemo to opet usporediti sa hudom jamom,

1313
00:51:27,539 --> 00:51:30,079
[SPEAKER_00] gdje su ljudi onako umirali u patnjama.

1314
00:51:30,079 --> 00:51:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, evo, taj logor Gakovu,

1315
00:51:33,079 --> 00:51:35,619
[SPEAKER_00] o njemu bi zaista trebalo snimiti.

1316
00:51:35,619 --> 00:51:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tamo gledao sam, imaju ovaj, kako se zove,

1317
00:51:38,000 --> 00:51:40,619
[SPEAKER_00] dva spomenika, tamo i nekad neko zabije neke tablice,

1318
00:51:40,619 --> 00:51:41,679
[SPEAKER_00] ja znam, tamo nekad otić.

1319
00:51:42,079 --> 00:51:43,579
[SPEAKER_00] I to je kao neko sjećanje,

1320
00:51:43,579 --> 00:51:44,820
[SPEAKER_00] onda dođe drugi dan, nemate tablice,

1321
00:51:44,820 --> 00:51:45,619
[SPEAKER_00] znači, bita aluminijska.

1322
00:51:45,619 --> 00:51:46,980
[SPEAKER_00] Možda neko dođe iz Njemačke,

1323
00:51:46,980 --> 00:51:48,360
[SPEAKER_00] pa ima neku baku ili nekoga,

1324
00:51:48,360 --> 00:51:50,840
[SPEAKER_00] zabije to da je to postoji nekako sjećanje,

1325
00:51:50,840 --> 00:51:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] da su tu i ti ljudi bili, kažem,

1326
00:51:52,539 --> 00:51:53,940
[SPEAKER_00] a njihova velika je tragedija,

1327
00:51:53,940 --> 00:51:55,360
[SPEAKER_00] što se smatra da su oni krivi.

1328
00:51:55,360 --> 00:51:56,699
[SPEAKER_00] A kažem, to su uglavnom...

1329
00:51:56,699 --> 00:51:58,800
[SPEAKER_01] Pa naravno, ljudi koji su živjeli na ovom prostoru,

1330
00:51:58,800 --> 00:52:00,199
[SPEAKER_01] koji opće nisu morali,

1331
00:52:00,199 --> 00:52:03,059
[SPEAKER_01] nisu, većina njih ništa nije imala

1332
00:52:03,059 --> 00:52:07,380
[SPEAKER_01] sa Hitlerom niti sa fašizmom niti sa Ićim.

1333
00:52:07,380 --> 00:52:09,119
[SPEAKER_00] Eto, bili su samo Njemci i to je to.

1334
00:52:09,119 --> 00:52:10,199
[SPEAKER_01] To je bilo dovoljno.

1335
00:52:10,199 --> 00:52:13,219
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ovaj model gdje se u stvari

1336
00:52:13,219 --> 00:52:17,059
[SPEAKER_01] dan do dana današnjeg radi ono što je protuzakonito,

1337
00:52:17,059 --> 00:52:21,039
[SPEAKER_01] to je da se veliča, dakle, zločin i komunizam.

1338
00:52:21,039 --> 00:52:23,960
[SPEAKER_01] To je ono što je problem današnje politike,

1339
00:52:23,960 --> 00:52:24,659
[SPEAKER_01] današnje države.

1340
00:52:24,659 --> 00:52:27,460
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ste ovo sad rekli kako maknu im te tablice,

1341
00:52:27,460 --> 00:52:31,119
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam bila nedavno u Laništu,

1342
00:52:31,260 --> 00:52:34,940
[SPEAKER_01] to je mjesto u kojem je ubijen Miroslav Bulešić,

1343
00:52:34,940 --> 00:52:36,860
[SPEAKER_01] blaženik hrvatski.

1344
00:52:36,860 --> 00:52:38,980
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ono što me tamo toliko iznenadilo,

1345
00:52:38,980 --> 00:52:40,599
[SPEAKER_01] to je spomen kući,

1346
00:52:40,599 --> 00:52:42,760
[SPEAKER_01] je da su ljudi koji su partizani,

1347
00:52:42,760 --> 00:52:44,340
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno vlast Jugoslavenska,

1348
00:52:44,340 --> 00:52:46,179
[SPEAKER_01] uhitila,

1349
00:52:46,179 --> 00:52:50,039
[SPEAKER_01] to su bili ljudi koji su branili svečenike

1350
00:52:50,039 --> 00:52:53,840
[SPEAKER_01] i na dan ubojstva Miroslava Bulešića

1351
00:52:53,840 --> 00:52:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ti ljudi koji su oni,

1352
00:52:56,000 --> 00:52:58,420
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, ubojica svečenika,

1353
00:52:58,420 --> 00:52:59,639
[SPEAKER_01] koji je ubio jednog svečenika,

1354
00:52:59,639 --> 00:53:00,619
[SPEAKER_01] premlatio drugog,

1355
00:53:01,019 --> 00:53:02,239
[SPEAKER_01] pokušao ubiti trećeg.

1356
00:53:02,239 --> 00:53:04,599
[SPEAKER_01] On je de facto nije bio kažnjen,

1357
00:53:04,599 --> 00:53:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] a ljude koji su branili,

1358
00:53:06,480 --> 00:53:08,840
[SPEAKER_01] su poslali u zatvor,

1359
00:53:08,840 --> 00:53:10,400
[SPEAKER_01] zajedno sa župnikom,

1360
00:53:10,400 --> 00:53:11,440
[SPEAKER_01] kojeg nisu uspjeli ubiti.

1361
00:53:11,440 --> 00:53:13,780
[SPEAKER_01] Među njima je bilo više ljudi

1362
00:53:13,780 --> 00:53:16,179
[SPEAKER_01] koji su bili u nacističkim logorima.

1363
00:53:16,179 --> 00:53:17,380
[SPEAKER_01] Jedan je bio u Dahoj.

1364
00:53:17,380 --> 00:53:21,099
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to su ljudi koji su doista bili antifašisti,

1365
00:53:21,099 --> 00:53:25,840
[SPEAKER_01] koji su završili u zatvorima fašističkim,

1366
00:53:26,179 --> 00:53:30,460
[SPEAKER_01] da bi ih onda komunisti uhitili i opet poslali u zatvor,

1367
00:53:30,460 --> 00:53:35,059
[SPEAKER_01] da je toga što nisu prihvaćali tu nepravdu prema crkvi i prema Hrvatima.

1368
00:53:35,400 --> 00:53:36,980
[SPEAKER_01] jer su oni bili Hrvati,

1369
00:53:36,980 --> 00:53:39,059
[SPEAKER_01] oni su se borili protiv italijanskih fašista.

1370
00:53:39,059 --> 00:53:41,639
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, a čovjek koji je ubojica,

1371
00:53:41,639 --> 00:53:42,980
[SPEAKER_01] dakle, Miroslav Bulešića,

1372
00:53:42,980 --> 00:53:44,860
[SPEAKER_01] njemu dan danas dolaze

1373
00:53:44,860 --> 00:53:47,340
[SPEAKER_01] antifašističke ove udruge

1374
00:53:47,340 --> 00:53:50,440
[SPEAKER_01] i uređuju mu grobi i veličaju ga.

1375
00:53:50,440 --> 00:53:51,800
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, čovjeka za kojeg se zna

1376
00:53:51,800 --> 00:53:53,179
[SPEAKER_01] da je bio ubojica,

1377
00:53:53,179 --> 00:53:54,920
[SPEAKER_01] da je ubio nekoga u miru,

1378
00:53:55,300 --> 00:53:55,780
[SPEAKER_01] nožem,

1379
00:53:55,780 --> 00:53:58,099
[SPEAKER_01] zato je došao na dodjeljivanje krizme.

1380
00:53:58,099 --> 00:53:59,579
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je,

1381
00:53:59,579 --> 00:54:02,900
[SPEAKER_01] to je fakat, ono, više sumanuto.

1382
00:54:02,900 --> 00:54:05,239
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, evo, recimo, kad to spominjete,

1383
00:54:05,239 --> 00:54:06,179
[SPEAKER_00] evo, mi imamo slučaj,

1384
00:54:06,179 --> 00:54:07,239
[SPEAKER_00] neka oni to rade,

1385
00:54:07,239 --> 00:54:08,760
[SPEAKER_00] evo, recimo, možemo se raditi opet na Mirgovi.

1386
00:54:08,760 --> 00:54:10,179
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, tu ima groblje partizansko,

1387
00:54:10,179 --> 00:54:12,119
[SPEAKER_00] tako zvane groblje Jugoslavijske armije

1388
00:54:12,119 --> 00:54:13,940
[SPEAKER_00] i to su uređeni grobovi, tako da.

1389
00:54:13,940 --> 00:54:15,059
[SPEAKER_00] A ima ovo drugo groblje,

1390
00:54:15,059 --> 00:54:15,860
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je moj stris.

1391
00:54:15,860 --> 00:54:18,980
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam danas bio na groblju

1392
00:54:18,980 --> 00:54:20,500
[SPEAKER_00] i križ je bio bačen danas.

1393
00:54:20,500 --> 00:54:21,739
[SPEAKER_00] Zna sam ga ponovno vratio nazad,

1394
00:54:21,739 --> 00:54:23,159
[SPEAKER_00] ali stalno se to događa.

1395
00:54:23,159 --> 00:54:24,400
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo joj sedmi križ stavili.

1396
00:54:24,400 --> 00:54:26,659
[SPEAKER_00] Jednostavno, oni boje se,

1397
00:54:26,659 --> 00:54:27,059
[SPEAKER_00] evo, recimo,

1398
00:54:27,059 --> 00:54:28,739
[SPEAKER_00] ne, boje se nama reći,

1399
00:54:28,739 --> 00:54:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] recimo, evo, sadašnji gradonači,

1400
00:54:30,380 --> 00:54:32,099
[SPEAKER_00] mi njemu, mi tražimo razgovor s njim.

1401
00:54:32,099 --> 00:54:33,260
[SPEAKER_00] Sa gospodinom Tomašević.

1402
00:54:33,260 --> 00:54:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, tražimo, pa dobre.

1403
00:54:34,000 --> 00:54:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] Zagovornikom ljudskih prava, da.

1404
00:54:35,960 --> 00:54:36,619
[SPEAKER_00] A zna samo to,

1405
00:54:36,619 --> 00:54:38,280
[SPEAKER_00] mi imamo sve legalne dozvole

1406
00:54:38,280 --> 00:54:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] da se groblje obnovi.

1407
00:54:39,440 --> 00:54:40,880
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, građevinsku dozvu, uporabnu,

1408
00:54:40,880 --> 00:54:42,679
[SPEAKER_00] suglasnost iz svih institucija

1409
00:54:42,679 --> 00:54:43,360
[SPEAKER_00] grada Zagreba,

1410
00:54:43,360 --> 00:54:44,880
[SPEAKER_00] pa čak i njegove institucije.

1411
00:54:44,880 --> 00:54:46,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, njegov grad Zagrebe

1412
00:54:46,039 --> 00:54:46,820
[SPEAKER_00] je dao suglasnost.

1413
00:54:46,820 --> 00:54:47,960
[SPEAKER_01] Nije grad Zagreb njegov,

1414
00:54:47,960 --> 00:54:48,619
[SPEAKER_01] hvala Bogu,

1415
00:54:48,619 --> 00:54:49,920
[SPEAKER_01] ali grad Zagrebe je dao.

1416
00:54:49,920 --> 00:54:51,219
[SPEAKER_00] Ali on predstavlja to.

1417
00:54:51,219 --> 00:54:52,679
[SPEAKER_00] I znači, dok je gospodin Bandić

1418
00:54:52,679 --> 00:54:53,440
[SPEAKER_00] bio gradonačenik,

1419
00:54:53,440 --> 00:54:55,800
[SPEAKER_00] on u stvari sve što je Bandić

1420
00:54:55,800 --> 00:54:56,219
[SPEAKER_00] potpisao,

1421
00:54:56,219 --> 00:54:57,199
[SPEAKER_00] bi trebao to poštivati.

1422
00:54:57,199 --> 00:54:59,300
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, gospodin Bandić

1423
00:54:59,300 --> 00:55:00,960
[SPEAKER_00] je bio gradonačenik grada Zagreba

1424
00:55:00,960 --> 00:55:02,500
[SPEAKER_00] i on samo nastavlja

1425
00:55:02,500 --> 00:55:03,119
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je on stao.

1426
00:55:03,119 --> 00:55:04,679
[SPEAKER_00] Nije to bio Milan Bandić

1427
00:55:04,679 --> 00:55:05,900
[SPEAKER_00] nego gradonačenik grada Zagreba.

1428
00:55:05,900 --> 00:55:07,280
[SPEAKER_00] Kao i on je Tomislav Tomašević,

1429
00:55:07,280 --> 00:55:08,280
[SPEAKER_00] on je za nas gradonačenik.

1430
00:55:08,280 --> 00:55:09,179
[SPEAKER_00] Preuzve obavezu

1431
00:55:09,179 --> 00:55:09,440
[SPEAKER_00] u grad Zagreba.

1432
00:55:09,440 --> 00:55:10,679
[SPEAKER_00] On je gradonačenik grada Zagreba.

1433
00:55:10,679 --> 00:55:11,179
[SPEAKER_00] On za mene nije

1434
00:55:11,179 --> 00:55:11,980
[SPEAKER_00] Tomislav Tomašević,

1435
00:55:11,980 --> 00:55:13,300
[SPEAKER_00] on je za mene gradonačenik

1436
00:55:13,300 --> 00:55:14,039
[SPEAKER_00] grada Zagreba.

1437
00:55:14,039 --> 00:55:15,280
[SPEAKER_00] I on jednostavno

1438
00:55:15,280 --> 00:55:16,739
[SPEAKER_00] ne želi s nama razgovarati.

1439
00:55:16,739 --> 00:55:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, oni, kažem,

1440
00:55:18,019 --> 00:55:19,699
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da je to prešučivanje

1441
00:55:19,699 --> 00:55:20,519
[SPEAKER_00] i ignoriranje.

1442
00:55:20,519 --> 00:55:21,679
[SPEAKER_00] Oni se time služe.

1443
00:55:21,679 --> 00:55:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ne žele razgovarati.

1444
00:55:24,079 --> 00:55:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] kažem, to groblje,

1445
00:55:25,699 --> 00:55:27,579
[SPEAKER_00] evo, mi već to 15 godina.

1446
00:55:27,579 --> 00:55:29,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ali svak vam čast na tome.

1447
00:55:29,139 --> 00:55:30,139
[SPEAKER_01] Zbiljam svak vam čast.

1448
00:55:30,139 --> 00:55:31,380
[SPEAKER_01] Znate šta mene

1449
00:55:31,380 --> 00:55:33,440
[SPEAKER_01] to podsjeća?

1450
00:55:33,440 --> 00:55:34,900
[SPEAKER_01] Na isto ovo što se događa

1451
00:55:34,900 --> 00:55:35,780
[SPEAKER_01] sad sa HOS-om.

1452
00:55:35,780 --> 00:55:38,579
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, metoda je bila

1453
00:55:38,579 --> 00:55:39,900
[SPEAKER_01] za vrijeme Jugoslavije,

1454
00:55:39,900 --> 00:55:41,340
[SPEAKER_01] za vrijeme totalitarnog režima

1455
00:55:41,340 --> 00:55:43,059
[SPEAKER_01] i danas ponovno to nastoje

1456
00:55:43,059 --> 00:55:45,380
[SPEAKER_01] da se mi odreknemo,

1457
00:55:45,380 --> 00:55:47,239
[SPEAKER_01] da se mi odreknemo ljudi

1458
00:55:47,239 --> 00:55:48,840
[SPEAKER_01] koji su nedužni

1459
00:55:48,840 --> 00:55:50,460
[SPEAKER_01] i da se prestanemo govoriti

1460
00:55:50,460 --> 00:55:51,340
[SPEAKER_01] u ime onih

1461
00:55:51,340 --> 00:55:52,619
[SPEAKER_01] koji su bili žrtve.

1462
00:55:52,900 --> 00:55:54,519
[SPEAKER_01] jer mi kad gledamo o taj HOS,

1463
00:55:54,519 --> 00:55:55,400
[SPEAKER_01] pa čovječe,

1464
00:55:55,400 --> 00:55:57,639
[SPEAKER_01] kako je normalan čovjek u Hrvatskoj,

1465
00:55:57,639 --> 00:55:59,679
[SPEAKER_01] ako se samo jedne stvari sjetimo,

1466
00:55:59,679 --> 00:56:00,880
[SPEAKER_01] a to je ovo što ste ispričali,

1467
00:56:00,880 --> 00:56:02,500
[SPEAKER_01] svjedočanstvo ljudi

1468
00:56:02,500 --> 00:56:04,219
[SPEAKER_01] kojima da su HOS-ovci

1469
00:56:04,219 --> 00:56:05,579
[SPEAKER_01] ulazili u Minsko polje

1470
00:56:05,579 --> 00:56:06,099
[SPEAKER_01] svoje žive,

1471
00:56:06,099 --> 00:56:07,260
[SPEAKER_01] pogine jedan,

1472
00:56:07,260 --> 00:56:08,519
[SPEAKER_01] odleti u zrak,

1473
00:56:08,519 --> 00:56:09,539
[SPEAKER_01] drugi ide napredi

1474
00:56:09,539 --> 00:56:10,739
[SPEAKER_01] svojim tijelom čisti polje

1475
00:56:10,739 --> 00:56:11,440
[SPEAKER_01] da prođu ljudi.

1476
00:56:11,440 --> 00:56:13,420
[SPEAKER_01] Kako ti možeš te ljude zanjekati?

1477
00:56:13,420 --> 00:56:15,360
[SPEAKER_01] Pa što si ti ako ih zanječeš?

1478
00:56:15,360 --> 00:56:16,500
[SPEAKER_01] Što smo mi ako mi kažemo

1479
00:56:16,500 --> 00:56:18,300
[SPEAKER_01] dobro, oni su bili fašisti?

1480
00:56:18,300 --> 00:56:18,639
[SPEAKER_01] Ne!

1481
00:56:22,900 --> 00:56:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] Evo Vukovar,

1482
00:56:23,539 --> 00:56:24,159
[SPEAKER_00] kad ste spomenuli,

1483
00:56:24,159 --> 00:56:25,360
[SPEAKER_00] jednog HOS-ovca,

1484
00:56:25,360 --> 00:56:26,059
[SPEAKER_00] Žani Kolija

1485
00:56:26,059 --> 00:56:27,639
[SPEAKER_00] i možemo Šljivančanina.

1486
00:56:27,639 --> 00:56:28,340
[SPEAKER_00] Koga bi ja izabrao?

1487
00:56:28,340 --> 00:56:28,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bi izabrao

1488
00:56:28,860 --> 00:56:29,519
[SPEAKER_00] da je Žani Kolija.

1489
00:56:29,519 --> 00:56:30,860
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno.

1490
00:56:30,860 --> 00:56:31,820
[SPEAKER_00] A oni biraju koga?

1491
00:56:31,820 --> 00:56:32,719
[SPEAKER_00] Oni biraju Šljivančanina.

1492
00:56:32,719 --> 00:56:33,599
[SPEAKER_01] A oni odabiraju Šljivančanina.

1493
00:56:33,599 --> 00:56:34,739
[SPEAKER_00] I oni kažu da Šljivančanin

1494
00:56:34,739 --> 00:56:35,800
[SPEAKER_00] borni bolje od Žani Kolija.

1495
00:56:35,800 --> 00:56:35,820
[SPEAKER_00] Tako.

1496
00:56:35,820 --> 00:56:38,159
[SPEAKER_01] I oni danas o HOS-u govore

1497
00:56:38,159 --> 00:56:40,559
[SPEAKER_01] ono što je 1991. Šljivančanin

1498
00:56:40,559 --> 00:56:41,219
[SPEAKER_01] o HOS-u govorio.

1499
00:56:41,219 --> 00:56:42,579
[SPEAKER_00] Crven kapa je pogino.

1500
00:56:42,579 --> 00:56:44,619
[SPEAKER_00] On je pogino znači u minjskom polju.

1501
00:56:44,619 --> 00:56:46,059
[SPEAKER_00] Znači on je svoje tijelo dao

1502
00:56:46,059 --> 00:56:46,780
[SPEAKER_00] da bi drugi živjeli.

1503
00:56:46,780 --> 00:56:48,219
[SPEAKER_00] On je dao svoj život

1504
00:56:48,219 --> 00:56:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] da bi drugi živjeli.

1505
00:56:49,380 --> 00:56:50,940
[SPEAKER_00] A to komunisti neće nikada.

1506
00:56:50,940 --> 00:56:51,260
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1507
00:56:51,260 --> 00:56:52,940
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, kažem,

1508
00:56:52,940 --> 00:56:54,519
[SPEAKER_00] između HOS-a

1509
00:56:54,519 --> 00:56:56,400
[SPEAKER_00] i Jugoslavijske narodne armije...

1510
00:56:56,400 --> 00:56:57,440
[SPEAKER_01] Nema dileme, je li tako?

1511
00:56:57,440 --> 00:56:58,300
[SPEAKER_00] Pa evo, ali mi smo na kraju

1512
00:56:58,300 --> 00:56:59,400
[SPEAKER_00] izabrali Jugoslavijske narodne armije.

1513
00:56:59,400 --> 00:56:59,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

1514
00:56:59,539 --> 00:57:00,639
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, ja nisam.

1515
00:57:00,639 --> 00:57:03,199
[SPEAKER_01] Mi nismo i nećemo.

1516
00:57:03,199 --> 00:57:04,719
[SPEAKER_01] I kao što...

1517
00:57:04,719 --> 00:57:06,059
[SPEAKER_00] Između HOS-a i Jena

1518
00:57:06,059 --> 00:57:06,980
[SPEAKER_00] zna se što biramo.

1519
00:57:06,980 --> 00:57:07,840
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, zna se.

1520
00:57:07,840 --> 00:57:09,320
[SPEAKER_01] Puna hvala gospodin Šola.

1521
00:57:09,320 --> 00:57:11,519
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala na ovom upornom bavljenju

1522
00:57:11,519 --> 00:57:12,360
[SPEAKER_01] ovom temom.

1523
00:57:12,360 --> 00:57:13,699
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala gospodinu Franoviću

1524
00:57:13,699 --> 00:57:17,920
[SPEAKER_01] koji tako želi i pomaže

1525
00:57:17,920 --> 00:57:20,360
[SPEAKER_01] financiranje ovakvih istraživanja

1526
00:57:20,360 --> 00:57:22,139
[SPEAKER_01] i svima vama koji ste aktivni udruzi

1527
00:57:22,139 --> 00:57:24,679
[SPEAKER_01] za promicanje istine

1528
00:57:24,679 --> 00:57:26,400
[SPEAKER_01] u Hrvatskoj povisti.

1529
00:57:26,400 --> 00:57:28,420
[SPEAKER_01] Jer to promicanje istine daje ploda

1530
00:57:28,420 --> 00:57:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] i daće ga u budućnosti.

1531
00:57:30,000 --> 00:57:30,400
[SPEAKER_00] Pa biće.

1532
00:57:30,400 --> 00:57:31,679
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ga. Hvala vama.

1533
00:57:31,679 --> 00:57:33,059
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vama, dragi gledatelji,

1534
00:57:33,059 --> 00:57:35,199
[SPEAKER_01] da ste nas pratili.

1535
00:57:35,320 --> 00:57:36,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ako imate kakvih pitanja

1536
00:57:36,360 --> 00:57:37,280
[SPEAKER_01] postavljajte ih.

1537
00:57:37,280 --> 00:57:39,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ako niste još zapratili moju stranicu

1538
